{"tid":1405633,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋罷交租 公屋罷交租","createTime":"2019-08-04T10:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T14:40:29.000Z","uid":189799,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1584e2abf7f633f928c2858835ae07891dc22648","tid":1405633,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:36:44.000Z","msg":"公屋問題一直咁多年都無解決，而且係一直惡化。<br />\n若果將戰線推埋去公屋度，可以爭取市民支持，亦可增加政府行政成本。<br />\n<br />\n-唔駛驚唔交租會收左你間房，正常嘅話佢會打電話提你，出信提你，若果無交3個月先出信話再唔交就收樓，到時先交就ok。<br />\n<br />\n-房署仲驚過你。因為佢地內部有指標，欠租率唔可以太低。<br />\n<br />\n-目標係增加房委會嘅財政壓力，增加政府行政成本。<br />\n<br />\n-希望推廣8月起唔交租，用自動轉帳嘅請cut。"},{"pid":"5792adb7ea66739328db5646b56f67e7fb130a43","tid":1405633,"uid":264908,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:42:09.000Z","msg":"為社會基層紓解開支壓力，好事一樁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa730f493fbb693120d01fe137f99e6e20f06ebe","tid":1405633,"uid":189799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:46:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a24c0473e00328762226282ced855a5ed3a077a7","tid":1405633,"uid":189799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:00:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3e5e9885914e35f4a1fa1227da8d245c1364dc3","tid":1405633,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:01:56.000Z","msg":"罷埋交稅就差唔多！"},{"pid":"e9973626055b85ceacd2beb63d40dae5c7c11b62","tid":1405633,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3e5e9885914e35f4a1fa1227da8d245c1364dc3","tid":1405633,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:01:56.000Z","msg":"罷埋交稅就差唔多！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:59:06.000Z","msg":"無咁快交稅，但租每個月都要交"},{"pid":"a1a242cbc924a472aa6dcea20343bae2a477f977","tid":1405633,"uid":18764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:01:12.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f98